      <title>Butterfly主题配置指南</title>
      <link href="/2025/08/20/Butterfly%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/"/>
      <url>/2025/08/20/Butterfly%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Butterfly主题配置指南"><a href="#Butterfly主题配置指南" class="headerlink" title="Butterfly主题配置指南"></a>Butterfly主题配置指南</h1><p>Butterfly是一款功能强大、美观大方的Hexo主题，本文将详细介绍如何安装和配置Butterfly主题，让你的博客焕然一新。</p><h2 id="安装主题"><a href="#安装主题" class="headerlink" title="安装主题"></a>安装主题</h2><h3 id="方法一：npm安装"><a href="#方法一：npm安装" class="headerlink" title="方法一：npm安装"></a>方法一：npm安装</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">npm install hexo-theme-butterfly<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="方法二：Git克隆"><a href="#方法二：Git克隆" class="headerlink" title="方法二：Git克隆"></a>方法二：Git克隆</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">git <span class="hljs-built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/jerryc127/hexo-theme-butterfly.git themes/butterfly<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="应用主题"><a href="#应用主题" class="headerlink" title="应用主题"></a>应用主题</h2><p>修改Hexo根目录下的 <code>_config.yml</code>：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">theme:</span> <span class="hljs-string">butterfly</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="安装必要插件"><a href="#安装必要插件" class="headerlink" title="安装必要插件"></a>安装必要插件</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">npm install hexo-renderer-pug hexo-renderer-stylus<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="主题配置"><a href="#主题配置" class="headerlink" title="主题配置"></a>主题配置</h2><h3 id="1-基本信息设置"><a href="#1-基本信息设置" class="headerlink" title="1. 基本信息设置"></a>1. 基本信息设置</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-comment"># 网站标题</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">title:</span> <span class="hljs-string">我的博客</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">subtitle:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;个人博客网站&#x27;</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">description:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;这是我的个人博客，记录生活和技术&#x27;</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">keywords:</span> <span class="hljs-string">博客,技术,生活</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">author:</span> <span class="hljs-string">我的名字</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">language:</span> <span class="hljs-string">zh-CN</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">timezone:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Asia/Shanghai&#x27;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-导航菜单设置"><a href="#2-导航菜单设置" class="headerlink" title="2. 导航菜单设置"></a>2. 导航菜单设置</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">menu:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-string">首页:</span> <span class="hljs-string">/</span> <span class="hljs-string">||</span> <span class="hljs-string">fas</span> <span class="hljs-string">fa-home</span><br>  <span class="hljs-string">归档:</span> <span class="hljs-string">/archives/</span> <span class="hljs-string">||</span> <span class="hljs-string">fas</span> <span class="hljs-string">fa-archive</span><br>  <span class="hljs-string">标签:</span> <span class="hljs-string">/tags/</span> <span class="hljs-string">||</span> <span class="hljs-string">fas</span> <span class="hljs-string">fa-tags</span><br>  <span class="hljs-string">分类:</span> <span class="hljs-string">/categories/</span> <span class="hljs-string">||</span> <span class="hljs-string">fas</span> <span class="hljs-string">fa-folder-open</span><br>  <span class="hljs-string">友链:</span> <span class="hljs-string">/link/</span> <span class="hljs-string">||</span> <span class="hljs-string">fas</span> <span class="hljs-string">fa-link</span><br>  <span class="hljs-string">关于:</span> <span class="hljs-string">/about/</span> <span class="hljs-string">||</span> <span class="hljs-string">fas</span> <span class="hljs-string">fa-heart</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-社交图标设置"><a href="#3-社交图标设置" class="headerlink" title="3. 社交图标设置"></a>3. 社交图标设置</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">social:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">fab fa-github:</span> <span class="hljs-string">https://github.com/yourusername</span> <span class="hljs-string">||</span> <span class="hljs-string">Github</span> <span class="hljs-string">||</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;#24292e&#x27;</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">fas fa-envelope:</span> <span class="hljs-string">mailto:your-email@example.com</span> <span class="hljs-string">||</span> <span class="hljs-string">Email</span> <span class="hljs-string">||</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;#4a7dbe&#x27;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-首页设置"><a href="#4-首页设置" class="headerlink" title="4. 首页设置"></a>4. 首页设置</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">index_img:</span> <span class="hljs-string">https://example.com/path/to/image.jpg</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="5-文章页面设置"><a href="#5-文章页面设置" class="headerlink" title="5. 文章页面设置"></a>5. 文章页面设置</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">post_meta:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">page:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">date_type:</span> <span class="hljs-string">both</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">categories:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">tags:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">post:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">date_type:</span> <span class="hljs-string">both</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">categories:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">tags:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="功能开启"><a href="#功能开启" class="headerlink" title="功能开启"></a>功能开启</h2><h3 id="1-本地搜索"><a href="#1-本地搜索" class="headerlink" title="1. 本地搜索"></a>1. 本地搜索</h3><p>首先安装插件：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">npm install hexo-generator-search --save<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后在主题配置文件中启用：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">search:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">use:</span> <span class="hljs-string">local_search</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">placeholder:</span> <span class="hljs-string">搜索文章...</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-代码高亮"><a href="#2-代码高亮" class="headerlink" title="2. 代码高亮"></a>2. 代码高亮</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">code_blocks:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">theme:</span> <span class="hljs-string">darker</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">copy:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-文章目录"><a href="#3-文章目录" class="headerlink" title="3. 文章目录"></a>3. 文章目录</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">toc:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">post:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">page:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">false</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">number:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-评论系统"><a href="#4-评论系统" class="headerlink" title="4. 评论系统"></a>4. 评论系统</h3><p>Butterfly支持多种评论系统，以Valine为例：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">comments:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">use:</span> <span class="hljs-string">valine</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">text:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br>  <br><span class="hljs-attr">valine:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">appId:</span> <span class="hljs-string">your-appId</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">appKey:</span> <span class="hljs-string">your-appKey</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="总结"><a href="#总结" class="headerlink" title="总结"></a>总结</h2><h2 id="Butterfly主题功能丰富，配置灵活，通过以上设置，你可以打造一个美观、实用的个人博客。更多高级配置请参考官方文档。itle-Butterfly主题配置指南date-2025-08-20-23-18-36tags"><a href="#Butterfly主题功能丰富，配置灵活，通过以上设置，你可以打造一个美观、实用的个人博客。更多高级配置请参考官方文档。itle-Butterfly主题配置指南date-2025-08-20-23-18-36tags" class="headerlink" title="Butterfly主题功能丰富，配置灵活，通过以上设置，你可以打造一个美观、实用的个人博客。更多高级配置请参考官方文档。itle: Butterfly主题配置指南date: 2025-08-20 23:18:36tags:"></a>Butterfly主题功能丰富，配置灵活，通过以上设置，你可以打造一个美观、实用的个人博客。更多高级配置请参考<a href="https://butterfly.js.org/">官方文档</a>。itle: Butterfly主题配置指南<br>date: 2025-08-20 23:18:36<br>tags:</h2>]]></content>
      
      
